item.title: About Me
item.description: I am a computer enthusiast who is passionate about solving problems and learning new things. I enjoy traveling and pursuing the undiscovered. My road trip to Yosemite Park Education High School When I was 15, I took a university entrance exam (SAT) and scored very well for my age. I was encouraged to apply to universities. Since I had already completed the required number of high school classes for graduation, continuing high school further seemed pointless to me.
